2131}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"the landmark\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She looked positively regal in a beaded, sparkling white evening gown, her hair pulled back into a bun.\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2276, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a beaded\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"white evening gown\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2242}, {\"ngram\": \"her hair\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"a bun\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She gesticulated muscularly while she hit each note.\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each note\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With two speakers flanking her, the image immediately evoked Eva Peron on her balcony-or, if you are gay like me, Patti LuPone singing \\\"Do not Cry for Me Argentina\\\" inEvita.\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2391, \"end\": 2400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eva_Per\\u00f3n\", \"score\": 0.999999983064754, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eva Peron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eva_Per\\u00f3n\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eva_Per\\u00f3n\"}, {\"begin\": 2444, \"end\": 2456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patti_LuPone\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Patti LuPone\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patti_LuPone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patti_LuPone\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two speakers\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2347}, {\"ngram\": \"the image\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2371}, {\"ngram\": \"her balcony\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2415}, {\"ngram\": \"Me Argentina\\\" inEvita\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During an instrumental break, s